    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4 for a Class II device at medium model influence and high decision consequence. The primary validation result demonstrates RH = 0.83 at the worst-case operating point, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. Secondary validation against the NIST VAD hemolysis reference dataset provides corroborating evidence for shear-stress prediction fidelity. The overall credibility assessment supports acceptance of the CFD model for the declared CPB COU at MRL 2.",
